name: Rock-A-Feller - Gold Series - Toro
additionalNotes: The Gold Series makes use of a dark Mexican San Andrés maduro wrapper; this leaf is joined by an Ecuadorian Habano binder and fillers of Nicaragua (Estelí, Jalapa, and Ometepe) and Pennsylvania Broadleaf. Limited in production, the Rock-A-Feller Gold Series cigars are crafted for the discerning palate. This amounts to a medium-plus intensity, hitting standout complexities of toasted oak, earth, black pepper, and sweet mocha.
